{
  "stem": "4764.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think my mother must have learnt-- taught me in Polish how to read and write so I could go to school and pick it up.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because I was-- obviously had enough marks to stay in the class.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I wasn't thrown out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But Paris was terrific.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This is really-- I mean, that was just great.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'll always love Paris, ever since.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I went back many times, whenever I could.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] We knew we'd lost all our family and we only had one sister left who lived in-- in America.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is what our aim was, to get there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was one part of France which I disliked tremendously.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a-- a-- you had to go to this office near the Place de la Concorde [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] for refugees to fill out papers and try to get-- immigrate somewhere, you see?",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you have to sit there for hours and hours and hours, in the sense that, you know, because you just have to wait your turn.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And by this time I was-- I was now no longer that sort of terribly obedient child.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went crazy sitting there waiting hours, after hour, after hour.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And to this day, I can never stand in a line, in a queue, waiting for tickets or anything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I go quite-- quite peculiar.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If you put me in a line, by the time I get to the front, I'm so sarcastic to the person that I just can't do it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because I spent weeks, and weeks, and weeks, standing-- sitting there without anything to do.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You can imagine, it's just a terrible thing to just stand there, or sit there, with your parents, with nothing to do, waiting, and waiting, and waiting.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
